modShortDescription: Now you can stack a lot more than normal with this 7DTD mod. Over 164 items added. Nothing exceeds the number 30.000 for valid reasons.
modDescription:
Now you can [stack](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-stack-size/) a lot more than normal with this 7DTD mod. Over 164 items added. Nothing exceeds the number 30.000 for valid reasons. Game can only count to that number.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/Robeloto/7D2D_A19_Modlets/tree/master/Robeloto_StackmoreItems_XL)** for A19  
**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/Robeloto/7D2D_A18.4_Modlets/tree/master/Robeloto_StackmoreItems_XL)** for A18

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/12229-robelotos-modlets/).
